lyrics.text:
Hili ‘a e la’ala
’ā
, ‘e tō ‘a e ‘uh
a
;
‘Alotāmaki ē, toki ‘afua;
‘Osi ‘a e faingata’a, ‘e faingofua;
Hili ‘a e vahanoa, hopo ki ‘uta;

Hili masiva ē, kae maʻu koloa;
Hili ‘a e vaivai, mālohi noa;
‘Osi ‘a e ‘itengia, tō mai ‘a e ʻofa;
Hili ‘a e ngāue, mālōlōā.

Hili ‘a e fakahē’i, foki ki ‘api;
Hili ‘a e ilifia, ‘a e ‘amanaki;
Hili ‘a e lo’imata, ‘a e malimali;
Hoko ‘a e fiefia ki he mamahi.

Hopo ‘a e maama ē hili po’uli;
Mui ‘a e ututa’u ki he tutuu’i;
‘Osi fa’itoka na, toe mo’ui;
Hili kolosi ē, maʻu ‘a e kalauni.
